Investment  Managers and Registered Reps
      Grow your  business with DUAL REGISTRATION
~We  serve those exceptional investment professionals who work directly in the  equity and debt markets as well as mutual funds, wrap accounts, and packaged  products.  For 23 years, McClurg Capital  has provided the tools for investment managers and independent financial  consultants to build their own branded franchises---an asset that can be sold,  bequeathed, or succeeded for the benefit of you and your family. 
~For the registered representative---Access  to all domestic and international capital markets---bond desk---an enviable  array of mutual fund families---research resources---clearing and custody  through Pershing, a division of The Bank of New York Mellon---world class  investment management platform---marketing assistance and web design---local back office, practice management and  set up.
~For the investment manager---All of the  above and AIMR compliant, quarterly performance reporting and  mailing---quarterly billing notifications and collections---state and federal  record keeping and compliance---A TURNKEY SOLUTION
