Our Philosophy





Home

 
McClurg Capital is confident that the demographics of the next ten years will yield to U.S. capital markets unprecedented accumulation of investment assets. This accumulation should occur from the following 
        major sources:

        • Continued appreciation of U.S. financial assets through healthy economic growth 

        • Increased savings and investment rates from the increasing numbers of older Americans

        • Legislative liberalization of IRA, Roth, 401k, and other innovative savings accounts to relieve pressure from the Social Security system

        • Continuing growth in individual contributions to company sponsored 401k or 403b retirement plans

        • Inheritance by the "baby boomers” of their parents' accumulated life-long savings, investments, and real 
        estate assets

        McClurg Capital serves investors who wish to use a full service brokerage and investment advisory firm. We build long term relationships with serious investors who expect to work with a highly trained securities professional versed in all aspects of wealth management and financial instruments.
      		Clients of McClurg Capital benefit from expert guidance and strategic advice for growth. 
 



