McClurg  Capital affords investors the choice of how they pay for investment guidance  and implementation.  Clients may chose to utilize our Full-Service Brokerage on a traditional pay as  you go commission basis; or elect a fee-based solution through our Registered Investment Advisory where we are  compensated based on a modest percentage of the assets in your account.  We think of our  client relationship as a “partnership in  performance”. Regardless of your preference, we assume a higher  level of accountability than that which is  otherwise found in a typical brokerage, bank, or mutual fund relationship. We  want to be your single source financial partner.
McClurg  Capital Corporation is a financial services company owned by dedicated,  experienced investment professionals of highest ethical standards.  Established in 1985 and headquartered in San  Rafael, California, McClurg Capital provides investment services and support to  help our clients achieve their financial goals   The firm offers its expertise to an elite corps of investors seeking  participation in unusual opportunities in undervalued assets, special growth  situations, and high quality fixed-income securities.  This brochure offers a profile of McClurg  Capital, its philosophy, capabilities, and innovative approach to the industry.








